RACE.FOOTNOTES: MINDSHARE away cleanly, cleared rivals on the backstretch, entered turn inside, drifted out into the two to three path, entered lane in the four path, kept to task and held sway. TAKEITTOTHEBANK away well, tracked pace along the inside, continued along the inside on the turn, entered lane in the two path, responded well to urging and finished a willing second. HOLYJAZZ settled off the pace on the backstretch, continued to trail entering the turn, asked midway on the turn, entered lane in the three path and made a mild rally to get up for third. UNTO THEE chased leader along the inside on the backstretch, continued along the inside on the turn, in range entering the lane and gave way approaching the final sixteenth. CLUBHOUSE CAT tracked pace off the rail on the backstretch, continued off the rail on the turn, entered lane widest and outfinished by rivals in the lane.
